{"tid":1039442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【御用外國人】「一哥」布偉傑離開無線 進軍荷李活","createTime":"2019-02-27T11:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T02:59:07.000Z","uid":185631,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c93b81e3bb5ee4f00a1f70f0fa50d00169890bc5","tid":1039442,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5rionx3QdkPEkUxdDirjhw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190227f155155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5rionx3QdkPEkUxdDirjhw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190227f155155.jpg&h=75141889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】無線御用外國人布偉傑操流利廣東話，於多套劇集中飾演外國人角色，其中最為人熟悉的是《同事三分親》扮演的韋一，從此大家就稱呼他做「一哥」。<br />\n<br />\n不過正因為他外國人的面孔，令他的發揮空間受限，每次在劇集中幾乎都飾演外國高層，角色已經被定型。布偉傑在剛開播的《福爾摩師奶》中亦有出現，但這套劇集是他的告別之作。<br />\n<br />\n他完成《荷里活有個大老千》和《福爾摩師奶》的拍攝後離開無線，並於經理人兼化妝師太太Celia介紹下，認識電影公司華誼兄弟的朋友，更接拍兩套電影，進軍荷里活發展。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>其實布偉傑懂得4種語言，包括廣東話、普通話、英語和柬埔寨語，大學時修讀中國文學及亞洲研究，認真是外表外國人，內里亞洲人。</strong>"},{"pid":"17491253c104698fbc587718191a1b2e2f6b8cb9","tid":1039442,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"內里亞洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n里你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db196d0fba185eec0af95e74f473dee6e5890ed","tid":1039442,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"520c9bb9b9407a3d16c73d59fdea16873347b3b3","tid":1039442,"uid":29017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"華誼兄弟傳媒股份有限公司，是中國大陸一家知名綜合性娛樂集團，由王中軍、王中磊兄弟在1994年創立。"},{"pid":"0c52add495cbaaf6f4ae11427fb1feda2da5fd57","tid":1039442,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"路人樣喎 去到荷里活都唔起眼"},{"pid":"f4e62a2a54d338af7866ec9280a4c5035d0dfc85","tid":1039442,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"龍～捲～風～～～～～～～～～"},{"pid":"1b5fb5550eb9a755916985b5b486fd968ae86dc1","tid":1039442,"uid":114725,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"佢真係對自己嘅演技咁有信心？"},{"pid":"0dc903fe2a87a21fc712389a1c1357ab31d3b86e","tid":1039442,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"番去拍av?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bed24539efb6c032d62914f24f41687728ce98","tid":1039442,"uid":189460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"佢之前幫大陸人落黎非法整容單野點"}]}